sentences: Rather than returning to Berlin Richard moved to New York where he began engineering at Sound On Sound recording studio where he worked with such acts as Outkast, Jay-Z, Usher, Edwin McCain, and Fountains of WayneOutkast won a Grammy Award for Album Of The Year for their album Speakerboxxx/The Love Below which Richard engineered parts of in 2003.

Rather than returning to Berlin Richard moved to New York where he began engineering at Sound On Sound recording studio where he worked with such acts as Outkast, Jay-Z, Usher, Edwin McCain, and Fountains of WayneOutkast won a Grammy Award for Album Of The Year for their album Speakerboxxx/The Love Below which Richard engineered parts of in 2003.
Richard received Billboard Award plaques in recognition for his work on mixing Prince's, LotusFlow3r Record, released in 2008, which peaked at #1 for top R&B/Hip-Hop albums on April 18, 2009.
